  "bodyMarkdown": "Everyone makes mistakes, big and small. There is no easy way to return within the Content Management system built into Salesforce B2C Commerce Cloud once you save a Content Asset. It is easy as pie to roll back changes to even months ago within many plugins and editors (including [Elementor](http://elementor.com), which I use for this blog.) This is most certainly a missing feature in Page Designer and Content Assets!\n\n![](/media/2022/revision-blog-12e6fdce00.jpg)\n\nRevisions in Elementor\n\n[Vote for this idea here](https://ideas.salesforce.com/s/idea/a0B8W00000GdVsJUAV/versioning-of-content-assets)",
